('MG10 COMBO','$ 89','Black and Gold','MG10 is a versatile mixer suitable for a wide range of users and applications. Input channels: 10 Line Inputs (4 mono, 3 stereo), 4 Mic Inputs with 48V phantom power and HPH per channel. Output channels: 2 ST, 1 MONITOR, 1 AUX send, 1 PHONES.','mg10.png','Simple 10W Combo',2.5,NULL,NULL,NULL),
