('MG15GR COMBO','$ 139','Black and Gold','The Marshall MG15GR 15W 1x8" Guitar Combo Amp offers guitarists an impressive range of tones and effects in a portable package. Four channels—clean, crunch, overdrive 1 and overdrive 2—provide a variety of tones from pristine cleans to heavy distortion.','mg15gr.png','The Best 10W Combo',4.9,NULL,NULL,NULL),
('MG30GFX COMBO','$ 189','Black and Gold','The Marshall MG30GFX is a 30W amp that captures the iconic Marshall sound. Featuring clean, crunch, OD1, and OD2 channels with customizable tones, it offers versatility for various playing styles. The 10” speaker delivers a powerful sound suitable for rehearsals and stage performances.','mg30gfx.png','Simple 30W Combo',2.3,NULL,NULL,NULL),
('MG500FX COMBO','$ 299','Black and Gold','The MG50GFX is loaded with pure Marshall tone. You get your choice of Clean, Crunch, OD1, and OD2 channels that you can shape with a 3-band EQ. You also get integrated reverb, delay, and digital effects. Best of all, each channel''s settings are storable and recallable.','mg500fx.png','Great 50W Combo',3.8,NULL,NULL,NULL),
('STUDIO JTM HEAD','$ 949','Black and Brass','From its legendary warm and smooth tone to blending the voices for a combination of crunch and clean, the Studio JTM brings the outstanding sound that Marshall is so well known for. The smaller scale of the Studio JTM gives players the power of the authentic Marshall tone, in a more compact design.','studiojtm.png','Just a Great Combo',4.6,NULL,NULL,NULL),
